name: Taffi
description: Street Cats of Vis is a project I founded on the island of Vis, in Croatia. Taffi is one of my land cats, rescued as a barely-alive anemic kitten from Wellington, the Vis town dump. All the land cats are spayed or neutered and have regular food, water and shelter. If you'd like to support this project, you can make a donation at streetcatsofvis.com (mention HEN if you do!)
